dollars) for Siasi to arrest the spread of malaria and deal with
other health and medical problems.
</P>
<P>
Ramos declared Siasi town a calamity area last week as more
deaths and cases of malaria were reported from the
epidemic-stricken municipality.
</P>
<P>
Some 310 patients have been confined at the Siasi Medical
School campus since the outbreak of the disease in January and
were being attended to by a medical team from hospitals and health
offices. 
</P>
