<HEADLINE> S. Africa's Reserves Rise in February </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
JOHANNESBURG, March 3 (Xinhua) -- South Africa's gold and
foreign exchange reserves rose by 10.75 percent in February to
30.9 billion Rand (6.27 billion U.S. Dollars), provisional data
from the South African Reserve Bank showed Tuesday.
</P>
