<HEADLINE> Hong Kong Stocks Close Higher </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, March 3 (Xinhua) -- Hong Kong stocks on Tuesday
rebounded for 106.62 points from Monday's closing figure which
stopped a consecutive three-day surge.
</P>
