The key Hang Seng Index rose 0.94 percent to close at 11,425.46
points on Tuesday.
</P>
<P>
The blue chip index rose 24.31 points, or 0.21 percent, to
register at 11,343.15 at the opening bell Tuesday morning.
</P>
<P>
