<HEADLINE> Floriculture School to Be Opened in Lusaka </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LUSAKA, March 3 (Xinhua) -- Some enterprising youths are to
open a floriculture school in Lusaka this month to teach general
flower arrangements, Zambia Daily Mail reported Tuesday.
</P>
<P>
One of the youths, Kennedy Luo, who is already in
