<P>
He said that "everything is in place, we have acquired some
space from where to conduct lessons, the teaching materials are
there and we are just organizing furniture."
</P>
<P>
Among things to be taught include office, bridal, presentation
arrangements, and wreaths. Lessons in landscaping shall also be
provided in the school, probably the first of its kind in Zambia.
</P>
<P>
Luo said the school will contribute to the alleviation of
youth unemployment and the people will be able to start their own
businesses once they have received formal training.
</P>
<P>
He said although flower arrangement is not a new concept in
the country it has not been fully exploited as a source of
income.
</P>
<P>
He expressed concern at the lack of funds for youth projects
in the country.
</P>
<P>
Luo was trained in flower arrangement in the former Zaire now
the Democratic Republic of Congo.
</P>
<P>
To diversify its economy, Zambia is attaching more and more
importance to non-traditional exports including floriculture
exports. 
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
</DOC>
