<HEADLINE> Thai Bourse Index up 1.55 Points </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BANGKOK, March 3 (Xinhua) -- The Stock Exchange of Thailand
(SET) index Tuesday gained 1.55 points from Monday to close at
539.72.
</P>
<P>
Some 234 million shares worth 5.09 billion baht (118 million
U.S. dollars) changed hands Tuesday.
</P>
<P>
The SET index Monday gained 9.75 points to close at 538.17.
</P>
