Last year, co-sponsored by the Gansu provincial government and
Lanzhou city government, the trade fair received 7,700
visitors. During the fair 79 contracts were concluded with a
contracted value of 5.47 billion yuan. The total turnover as a
result of the trade fair was more than 1.5 billion yuan.
</P>
<P>
In recent years, the province has launched more projects to
develop non-ferrous metals, mineral resources and chemical
materials by taking the advantage of its rich natural
resources. 
